"Okay! Based on your message, I understand that you want me to provide you with a list of three parameters:

1. Misura: pressione, frequenza, entrambi (pressione e frequenza)
2. Quantit√†: 0 (today), 1 (yesterday), 7 (last week), 30 (last month), 365 (total)

Please let me know which parameter you would like to see, and I will provide the information accordingly." "GENERALE -1 LISTA"
